  "title": "Example on how to use Pagination (Connector / Widget) in React Native",
  "body": "Hello,\r\n\r\nI could use the connectCurrentRefinements correctly because I found a working example but I can't figure how to use the connectPagination in React Native.\r\n\r\nI can import it like the CurrentRefinements\r\n`import { connectCurrentRefinements, connectPagination } from \"react-instantsearch/connectors\";`\r\n\r\nI can use it like this : \r\n`const ConnectedPagination = connectPagination(Pagination);`\r\n\r\nBut then I don't know what to do. How are we suppose to create a component to use the props available ? (https://community.algolia.com/react-instantsearch/widgets/Pagination.html)\r\n\r\nI'm confused and new to this. Any help, advice ?\r\n\r\nThank you",
